Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's him, Porchemy-san!\N--He stole the money from us! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it easier for us \Nby coming here voluntarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We were having a hard time \Nmaking your friend talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Porchemy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It kind of hurts. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what happens \Nwhen you mess with adults?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight you! Sabo, help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a sword! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he got the knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Porchemy-san, that kid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When I come to face someone, I won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?! You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it! He's not like \Nthe thugs in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Enough playing \Naround! That's our money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back to us peacefully, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You must been possessed by \Nsome evil spirit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the money back so you won't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have better plans for that money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so reckless! \NWhy are you always like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm beaten by kids, I may \Nas well quit being a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--We'll make sure you quit!\N--We'll make sure you quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the whole story, \NPorchemy. How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you honestly get beaten by kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Captain Bluejam... The money is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me! I don't \Neven want to see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who will get my money back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me we'll let \Nit go without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. We'll get it back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a bad habit, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When faced with a real \Npirate it's best to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have such a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't feel right. \NI liked the one I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a stupid mistake. \NThe Bluejam clan won't forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll come after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was scary! \NI thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying! Shut up! \NStop crying already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like cowards or people who cry a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,--You...!\N--Whoa, he's just being thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you cough it \Nup in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're kind of people who'd kill \Nwomen or kids without hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I said anything... \Nyou wouldn't be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than dying, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you wanna become my friend that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I give you a hard time until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you follow me this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have nobody else to trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back to Windmill Village \Nand I don't like the mountain bandits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't follow you, I'd be all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Being lonely is more \Npainful than getting hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa is all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it easy for you when I'm around?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's hard without me?\N--Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Gold Roger had a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that there isn't such a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be some kind of devil \Nwho'd be better off dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't like spoiled kids like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not spoiled! I'm strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong?! You're not strong \Nat all! You cry like a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever gotten hit by \Na spiky thing? I'm only 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When I become your age - 10, I'll \Nstop crying and become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't cry even if I were \N7, stupid! I'm not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become stronger than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Shanks that I'd \Nbecome a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,--You? Become a pirate?\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--No way!\N--Yes way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, by the way, I have a little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--What? A problem?\N--Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluejam and the others will try to kill the \Nthree of us after this for sure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This forest that I've been living is close to where they are - Pirate's Bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they attack me when \NI fall asleep exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're gonna die.\N--Yeah, you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, huddle up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they wounded? They're all bandaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Boss! Boss! We have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? It's still early. What's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,1, 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,1, 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, Luffy... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, Luffy... Huh? Ace, Luffy... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace... Luffy... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, Luffy, huh? Ace, Luffy, \Nhuh? Ace, Luffy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Luffy! Who is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still early - you're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How come there is one more kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sabo! Hey, you must be Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo? I've heard your name before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? That makes it easier! Thank \Nyou for taking care of me from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Taking care"? Don't tell me \Nthat you're gonna stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't answer me with a fart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be kidding! I heard that \Nyou're a worthless brat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? I heard that you're \Na worthless old bag, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unnecessary information!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna look after one more brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard that you're a good worthless \Nold bag because you can't refuse a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you're a truly \Nmanly worthless old bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Truly manly"? I'm a woman! \NI'm not a gender bender!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, Luffy, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you a place to stay! \NYou gotta get to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--See ya!\N--See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy! You stay here and do \Nsome laundry and clean the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ace, Sabo, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! What annoying brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're gone, the Bluejam \Nclan might come by so be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bluejam clan might come by? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we beat some of his crew up! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dadan sure is an understanding \Nworthless old bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still a worthless old bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus she's a mountain bandit \Nand her face is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, so you ate the Devil Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you can have this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too kind, Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what fruit did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum? Gum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for the ability to swim, \Nyour body turned to rubber? So crappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not crappy! I can use \Na lot of unbeatable attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You have such a fat mouth even \Nthough you can't catch a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body really is rubber! Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play with my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But rubber surely stretches \Nand shrinks and expands so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...maybe it's useful when you're fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?! Oh yeah, I came \Nup with another attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called "Gum-Gum Balloon"! I can \Ndeflect cannonballs and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Can you do it for me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll do it just for \Nyou! Ace can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What is it?! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! You're getting bigger and bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...Balloon! See it?! It's cool, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think it's cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good for working off my meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo, kick it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the unbeatable attack \Nthat will deflect cannonballs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you deflect my kick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wait! You can't just eat and run!\N--Wait! You can't just eat and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--You bastard!\N--You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--Take this!\N--Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:19:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what can I say? Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! I almost got eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. You can have a lot \Nof crocodile meat for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I forgive you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat the crocodile already. \NI can't wait until dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! I wanna check something quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--Did you find it?\N--Look carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that we moved the "pirate savings".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna check Gray Terminal, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay. Why don't you go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't listen to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are hooligans from the city \Nand Bluejam's people everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that Bluejam got really frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! The kids that you're \Nlooking for are all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! You can't run from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that they bought \Nover pops at the Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better lay low for a \Nwhile until things calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? We'll just fight if they find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true but we don't have \Nto look for trouble ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluejam... The kids made quite an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that they're gonna find \Nthis place and come by pretty soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way that we can defeat them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is the end of the Dadan family!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say goodbye to the \Nhumble-but-sweet mountain bandit's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to quit the mountain bandit \Nbusiness than to get exterminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"We can't defeat them"? \N"Out of business"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic you guys are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you take pride in \Nbeing a mountain bandit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If they come by,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we can just hand Ace and \Nthe other two over to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But, boss, how do we explain it to Garp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, Bluejam is not the kind of guy who \Nwill be satisfied by just handing them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just pretend that \Nwe don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, try it! We gotta practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, are Ace and Sabo \Nhere? Just spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrible liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss! Ace and the other two are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace's close friend Sabo \Nstarted to live with them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,after being forced to \Nleave Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, Sabo, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,These three soon began spending their time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,fighting with wild animals in \Nthe mountain and in the jungle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and with hooligans from the city and pirates at the bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the people at \Nthe center of the kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,came to know their wrongdoing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The names of Luffy, Ace, and Sabo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.89,0:23:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,gradually gain fame among \Nthe thugs in the town.
